Package de.oth.blocklib.networking.nio

Class NetworkPacket

java.lang.Object
de.oth.blocklib.networking.nio.NetworkPacket
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
ConnectionStatePacket, MessagePacket, ReliableNetworkPacket
public abstract class NetworkPacket
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
Defines the basic structure of a packet that is transmitted over the network.
A packet encapsulates a set of coherent data sent together with control fields which are needed by the network stack.
Since:
2020
Author:
Matthias Wagner, Philipp Dormeier (HSP-SoSe 2020 Network)
